WEBVTT

01:36:31.942 --> 01:36:33.775
Mr. Ex-police.

01:36:34.567 --> 01:36:36.234
You deserve something
worse than a suspension.

01:36:37.025 --> 01:36:38.734
I want to punish you real bad.

01:36:39.150 --> 01:36:42.192
That is why I kidnapped two
of your favourite people.

01:36:43.067 --> 01:36:45.525
I have kept them in
two different places...

01:36:45.859 --> 01:36:48.400
but I'll murder them at the same time.

01:36:48.692 --> 01:36:50.609
Use your police brains...

01:36:50.900 --> 01:36:52.900
and try to save at least
any one of them.

01:36:53.400 --> 01:36:54.567
I'll give you a clue.

01:36:55.025 --> 01:36:56.692
The location where I'm
going to murder them...

01:36:56.984 --> 01:36:58.859
is what I have sketched
and left in a piece of paper.
